# game/Scenes/Mari/mari11.rpy:13
translate spanish mari11_e409c46b:

    # fr "I've been meaning to tell you about something."
    fr "Llevaba tiempo queriendo contarte algo."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari11.rpy:14
translate spanish mari11_3e3148de:

    # fr "I'm going to be quitting my job at Jackson's pretty soon."
    fr "Voy a dejar mi trabajo en Jackson's muy pronto."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari11.rpy:15
translate spanish mari11_9ecf0858:

    # pc "Oh, really? Not liking it anymore?"
    pc "¿En serio? ¿Ya no te gusta?"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari11.rpy:17
translate spanish mari11_db0440ee:

    # fr "Oh, no. Nothing like that. I'm kind of sad about having to leave, actually."
    fr "No, nada de eso. La verdad es que me da un poco de pena tener que irme."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari11.rpy:18
translate spanish mari11_c245c716:

    # fr "But I'm going to start my internship at the vet clinic over the summer and I won't have time to work at the restaurant anymore."
    fr "Pero voy a empezar mis prácticas en la clínica veterinaria este verano y ya no tendré tiempo para trabajar en el restaurante."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari11.rpy:20
translate spanish mari11_5d7fccaf:

    # fr "If I could find somebody to take my position, I would probably quit now, but Jackson hasn't been able to find another good waitress."
    fr "Si encontrara a alguien que ocupara mi puesto, probablemente dejaría el trabajo ahora mismo, pero Jackson no ha conseguido encontrar otra buena camarera."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari11.rpy:21
translate spanish mari11_16743130:

    # fr "And I don't want to just leave him without anybody, you know?"
    fr "Y no quiero dejarlo sin nadie, ¿sabes?"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari11.rpy:23
translate spanish mari11_dc3519a2:

    # fr "But it's exciting, moving on to a new thing. I'm sad about leaving some things behind, but happy to move forward."
    fr "Pero es emocionante pasar a algo nuevo. Me entristece dejar algunas cosas atrás, pero estoy contenta de seguir adelante."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari11.rpy:24
translate spanish mari11_7852f03d:

    # pc "Yeah, that's great. I'm proud of you."
    pc "Sí, eso es genial. Estoy orgulloso de ti."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari11.rpy:25
translate spanish mari11_351906a2:

    # fr "Thanks, [pcname]."
    fr "Gracias, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari11.rpy:27
translate spanish mari11_1d372568:

    # fr "And if you happen to know of anybody looking for a job, maybe point them towards Jackson's."
    fr "Y si por casualidad conoces a alguien que esté buscando trabajo, quizá podrías recomendarle Jackson's."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari11.rpy:28
translate spanish mari11_ec895fb6:

    # fr "The work isn't always fun, customers can be a pain sometimes, but Jackson has always been good to me and is a nice person to work for."
    fr "El trabajo no siempre es divertido, los clientes a veces pueden ser un rollo, pero Jackson siempre se ha portado bien conmigo y es una persona agradable para la que trabajar."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari11.rpy:29
translate spanish mari11_41de96df:

    # pc "I'll keep an eye out."
    pc "Estaré atenta."

translate spanish strings:

    # game/Scenes/Mari/mari11.rpy:2
    old "Stay the night at Mari's house."
    new "Quédate a pasar la noche en casa de Mari."

    # game/Scenes/Mari/mari11.rpy:3
    old "When you're lying in bed with her at night, she'll talk to you about this."
    new "Cuando estés en la cama con ella por la noche, te hablará de esto."

